(1) To run quarto do

`quarto preview bayesian-crash-course-vaw.qmd`

this will open a tab in Firefox.

(2) To compile it to html, use

`quarto render bayesian-crash-course-vaw.qmd --to html`

(3) to publish it to gh-pages (this will automatically push to github after the build)

`quarto publish gh-pages bayesian-crash-course-vaw.qmd`

(4) compile it via github actions, hand trigger the workflow at:

https://github.com/mauro3/BayesianCrashCourseVAW.jl/actions/workflows/render-qmd.yaml
